Plaintiffs have no objection to staying the consideration of this motion until this Court
deems appropriate. Indeed, Defendants still have not produced basic discovery relating to
Plaintiffs’ class claims. Once Plaintiffs have received the discovery to which they are entitled,
they may supplement this motion with additional evidence supporting class certification.
WHEREFORE, Plaintiffs respectfully request that this Court certify this suit as a class
action for prospective relief as set forth above and in the accompanying memorandum of law and
grant such other relief as the Court may deem appropriate.
Respectfully submitted,
